A '''Silver Feather of Bravery''' was a sacred item presented to young [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]] of [[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]] who had traveled to the [[Tree of Light]] and sprinkled it with [[Light Dust]]. The Feathers were presented as part of the [[Light Festival]] in honor of the Tree of Light and its power over the [[Night Spirit/Legends|Night Spirit]].

